         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">21/1/86 ¶  ¶ Enclosed I am sending you, noble Friend, a small reptile from  ¶ Central ¶  Australia. The little creature is of extraordinary agility, lives more on bushes than on the flat earth, and ru...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">86. 01.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Ferdinand von Krauss</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Staatliches Museum für Naturkunde, Stuttgart.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">MS annotation by Krauss: 'Empf. 8 März.86. zugleich 1 Blechschachtel mit 1 kl. </seg>Eidechsbalg. Varanus varians. Physignathus longirostris […] Rep. 28. <seg style="">Apr 86 Wo ist Sabai in N. Guinea? Bitte um Fruchtformen.' </seg>[Received 8 March 86 at the same time 1 tin box with 1 small lizard skin. <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Varanus variens. Physignathus longirostris</seg> […] <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Replied 28 April 86 Where is Sabai in New Guinea? Request about fruit forms.] Letter not found.</p>
               </note>21/1/86.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hierbei sende ich Ihnen, edler Freund, einen kleinen Saurier, aus </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Central</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Australien. Das Thierchen ist von ausserordentlicher Agilität, lebt mehr auf Sträuchern als auf ebener Erde, u. läuft auf den Hinterbeinen ebenso schnell als auf allen Vieren. Es hascht behende allerlei fliegende Insekten, u. ist daher ein sehr nützliches Thier.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Stets der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Letzte</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Woche sandte ich auch Einiges durch Tate's Agency an Sie ab.</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation: 'Angek. d. 16 März 86' [Arrived 16 March 1886].</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21/1/86</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed I am sending you, noble Friend, a small reptile from <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Central</hi>
               </seg> Australia. The little creature is of extraordinary agility, lives more on bushes than on the flat earth, and runs on the hind legs just as quickly as on all four. It nimbly snaps up all kinds of flying insects and is therefore a very useful animal.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Last</hi>
               </seg> week I also sent off some things to you through Tate's agency.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Frederick Tate.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
